# Response headers for the contractor portal (Cloudflare Workers static assets).
# The portal is ONE HTML file (everything else loads from CDNs at runtime), so
# always revalidate the shell with the server (cheap 304 via ETag) — a new
# deploy then shows up immediately, no hard refresh needed.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
